{"id":"sallu","term":"Sallu","source":"Easton's Bible Dictionary (M.G. Easton, 1897)","html":"<p>Weighed. (1.) A priest (<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Nehemiah 12:7\">Neh. 12:7</a>).</p>\n<p>(2.) A Benjamite (<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"1 Chronicles 9:7\">1 Chr. 9:7</a>; <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Nehemiah 11:7\">Neh. 11:7</a>).</p>\n\u0000","refs":["Nehemiah 12:7","1 Chronicles 9:7","Nehemiah 11:7"]}